{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762536575,"sessionID":"ses_126add179ffeFYyiaZOsieAbUe","part":{"id":"prt_ed952b0aa0010G37WCgenFmlVy","messageID":"msg_ed952a432001HBdtQbZsmuFmEJ","sessionID":"ses_126add179ffeFYyiaZOsieAbUe","type":"text","text":"The memory trigger preflight rejected the provided lineage session as non-server-managed, so I’m retrying the preflight without binding that MCP session. The review lineage session id will still be used in the artifacts as instructed.","time":{"start":1781762535594,"end":1781762536573},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0c243d753560dd3b016a3389e79098819184bec1b84e12105a","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781762550801,"sessionID":"ses_126add179ffeFYyiaZOsieAbUe","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_fFnGZSd7v2hjogcrZ2y7C4el","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-review agent running a fan-out lineage.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/B-rest-of-002\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-5\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55r2-b-5-1781761339355-o7qylx\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: review\n  config.maxIterations: 1\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop, and phase_synthesis. Bind artifact_dir directly to config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir. Write all outputs only under the lineage artifact directory. When complete, output FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55r2-b-5","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/B-rest-of-002","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":false},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"No matching trigger phrases found\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"count\": 0,\n    \"results\": [],\n    \"matchType\": \"trigger-phrase\",\n    \"degradedMatching\": null,\n    \"triggerSignals\": [],\n    \"cognitive\": null\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Ensure memories have trigger phrases defined\",\n    \"Try a different prompt or check memory content\",\n    \"[session] Context quality is CRITICAL. Consider ru