       \"title\": \"Fable-5 Governor — Reason Outward, Act, Commit, Qualify Minimally\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — do not audit the audit. | Prioritize when: the caveat changes what the reader should do — once, in the fewest words.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18038,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/deep-skill-workflow-required.md\",\n          \"title\": \"DEEP SKILLS — Use the Workflow, Never Hand-Roll\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Never Hand-Roll\\\" | Prioritize when: Never Hand-Roll\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16266,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never a grep narrowed to your own files — and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {…} → now M: {…}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No r…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16265,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch — Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retr