ever a grep narrowed to your own files — and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {…} → now M: {…}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No r…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15814,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch — Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsi… | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn — NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use exp…\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"triggered\": [\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6626,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename\",\n          \"title\": \"Skill Rename [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"skill\",\n            \"workflows\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"system\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7589,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit\",\n          \"title\": \"System-Spec-Kit Architecture Audit v2 [system-spec-kit/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/005-architecture-audit/research]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"system\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"research\",\n            \"005\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 7426,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/021-spec-kit-phase-system\",\n          \"title\": \"Verification Checklist: SpecKit Phase System [system-spec-kit/021-spec-kit-phase-system/checklist]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"verification\",\n            \"phase\",\n            \"system\",\n            \"021\",\n            \"spec\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 6623,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename\",\n          \"title\": \"Verification [system-spec-kit/z_archive/001-fix-command-dispatch/z_archive/007-system-spec-kit-rename/checklist]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"verification\",\n            \"workflows\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"kit\",\n            \"system\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"memory_id\": 8550,\n          \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/z_archive/024-compact-code-graph/005-command-agent-alignment\",\n          \"title\": \"Phase 5: Command & Agent Alignment [system-spec-kit/024-compact-code-graph/005-command-agent-alignment/spec]\",\n          \"matched_phrases\": [\n            \"phase\",\n            \"agent\",\n            \"spec\",\n            \"005\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-18T06:02:25.943Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 2648\n    },\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1781762543292,"end":1781762550799}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0c243d753560dd3b016a3389e885f08191acab3b691fd4e1f5"}},"id":"prt_ed952b47e001hxapiijOGGWvSz","sessionID":"ses_126add179ffeFYyiaZOsieAbUe","messageID":"msg_ed952a432001HBdtQbZsmuFmEJ"}}
