{"type":"text","timestamp":1781762631200,"sessionID":"ses_126add179ffeFYyiaZOsieAbUe","part":{"id":"prt_ed9541bd60013x7DUenSunE6h4","messageID":"msg_ed953fe7b001SfABvU5ik1K0B7","sessionID":"ses_126add179ffeFYyiaZOsieAbUe","type":"text","text":"One high-risk candidate is the atomic save ordering: the helper writes a pending file, calls the indexer, and only then promotes the pending file. I’m checking the caller and indexer contract before recording it as a finding.","time":{"start":1781762628566,"end":1781762631197},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_095b0222ed27f7d6016a338a4484188191897ca9479b3245d1","phase":"commentary"}}}}
